Optimize trees op bit ops to the following canonical form.

#### And
```SystemVerilog
/*from*/ ~a[2] & a[1] & ~a[0]
/*to*/ 3'b010 == (3'b111 & a)
```

```SystemVerilog
/*from*/ ~a[3] & (4'b0010 == (4'b0111 & a))
/*to*/ 4'b0010 == (4'b1111 & a)
```

### Or

```SystemVerilog
/*from*/ ~a[2] | a[1] | ~a[0]
/*to*/ 3'b101 != (3'b111 & a)
```

```SystemVerilog
/*from*/ ~a[3] ! (4'b0101 != (4'b0111 & a))
/*to*/ 4'b1010 != (4'b1111 & a)
```

### Xor

```SystemVerilog
/*from*/ ~a[2] ^| a[1]^| a[0]
/*to*/ ~(^(3'b111 & a))
```

```SystemVerilog
/*from*/ ~a[3] ^ ~(^(4'b0111 & a))
/*to*/ ^(4'b1111 & a)
```

